Package io.jeo.data

Data access.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Dataset
    A geospatial dataset.
    Disposable
    Interface for objects that should be closed after usage.
    Driver<T>
    Format driver.
    DriverRegistry
    Interface for registry for drivers.
    FileData
    Interface implemented by Dataset and Workspace objects that are file based.
    Transaction
    Transaction object.
    Transactional
    Interface implemented by Datasets that support transactions.
    Workspace
    A container of Dataset objects.
    WriteCursor
    Interface to be implemented by Cursor that provide write access.

    Driver utility class.
    FileDriver<T>
    Base class for file based drivers.
    Handle<T>
    Reference to a data object.
    ServiceLoaderDriverRegistry
    Loads drivers with ServiceLoader.
    SingleWorkspace
    Workspace implementation that contains a single dataset instance.
    Sort  
    StaticDriverRegistry
    Driver registry that uses a static list of driver objects.
